{"tid":2503580,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"痴撚線由Error到Mirror 柳b 呂b 依家我愛上埋Anson Kong","createTime":"2021-04-25T07:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T07:22:08.000Z","uid":3206,"like":123,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"8a547ca6e74f7b5a6a74080176f56087e1fa9134","tid":2503580,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T07:50:12.000Z","msg":"起我底就知我係因為睇完Error遊鍾意咗佢哋4個，再專登睇造星1睇佢哋參賽<br />\n然後唔小心鍾意咗Mirror各個成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解咁有星味咁有魅力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明之前睇佢哋啲相都覺柒下柒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算姜濤我都無feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再睇埋Mirror go<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 姜b好小朋友好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴撚線點解佢哋可以感情好成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解咁痴線咁玩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛上埋edan b<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再好奇睇下d mv  愛上咗jer仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實成隊人都幾鍾意但會想睇jer仔edan同姜b多d<br />\n<br />\n好啦追撚完開始睇造星2<br />\n<br />\n開頭以為佢哋係亂入幫手做表演，點知係用d咁嘅形式入去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有驚喜姐姐喜歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到Anson Kong喺台上面chok樣  屌唔小心俾佢電親<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個眼神同班參賽者高下立見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解可以咁撚型架！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io